        e: 'Angles accumulate: link 2 is rotated by theta1+theta2 in the world frame.' },
      { q: 'Maximum reach of the 2-link arm occurs when:',
        o: ['theta2 = 180 deg (folded)', 'theta2 = 0 (links aligned)', 'theta1 = 90 deg', 'L1 = 0'], a: 1,
